                    I have experience primarily
                    with JS, React, Java, C, and Python. </p>
                <!-- </div> -->
            <!-- </div> -->
        </div>

        <div class="md:pr-2 lg:pr-0 md:pt-18 text-2xl grid md:place-content-center">
            <img class="animate-zoom-in-slow rounded-full border border-dotted md:scale-90 lg:scale-150 lg:mt-12 lg:ml-0 lg:m-12" 
            src='/assets/alfonso3.png'  />
            <div id="socials" class="socials flex justify-center content-center md:pt-8">
                
                <div class="text-stone-400 pt-3">
                    <a href={`mailto:${contacts[1].contact}`} class="" >
